Anonymize both the key and value of a newline-delimited JSON file.
The anon_map is used to keep track of the (key -> anon_key) mapping.

anon_map := {
    key: anon_entry,
    ...
}
anon_entry := {
    'anon_key': anonymous_key,
    'anon_map': anon_map,
    'next_anon_key': next_key
}
